race.comment: REGGIE RANGOON (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.41) at this track behind Melania Banner in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Can go on with it. CAN'T HURRY LOVE (2) copped a check in the run last time and never threatened when eighth (23.77) in a Grade 5 at this track. Worth following up. ANJO TOPAZ (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 18.22 beating Near Impossible. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. LUCIA POWER (3) returns here as an each-way chance.
